T1  - Agreeing on disagreement: Heterogeneity or uncertainty?
AU  - ter Ellen, Saskia
AU  - Verschoor, Willem F.C.
AU  - Zwinkels, Remco C.J.
JO  - Journal of Financial Markets
VL  - 44
SP  - 17
EP  - 30
